commit e2fea298517101fdd5ad8c094bf6d341f5415a47
Author: unknown <Shlomy@.(none)>
Date:   Mon Sep 20 04:37:07 2010 +0200

    Fixed bug #3071356 - NPE from DirtyGutter.
    The NPE is caused by the fact that buffer listeners are called before the buffer is loaded, and trying to get the buffer's text at this stage causes an NPE because the buffer has a line count of 1 but its text is null (not an empty string).

